{"tid":2452832,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"青衣/荃灣區電結他招生, 教jazz亦教rock 3","createTime":"2021-03-19T05:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:19:30.000Z","uid":166708,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"faed0f00eb896793fdd07babd40f79c80dc19d4b","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"Hello, 相信疫情期間,做音樂做藝術的同行都相信挨得好辛苦,大家堅持緊的請加油<br />\n<br />\n咁好興幸呢兩年都死唔去, 不過琴行果邊由7個變 3個, 教兩日變教一日<br />\n<br />\n私人有人移民,有人畢業,有人失業無錢學落去,都幾Sad<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, the time must go on,<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個係今屆的8級學生, 兩個都慶幸MERIT,<br />\n<br />\n有一個係上次招生post 兩年前 跟我學的<br />\n<br />\n佢本身有古典樂好濃厚的底,所以做到兩年8級merit,咁當然佢的努力係絕大部分<br />\n<br />\n佢可以短時間就識大部分jazz standard 的中階曲 如: All of me, blue bossa, night and Day<br />\n<br />\n再加JAMMING得唔錯 同唔同曲風 呢個後生仔認真唔錯<br />\n<br />\n另外一個都好好, 由零開始,跟左幾年到姐, 都一樣識睇五線譜, 識jazz standard同jamming<br />\n<br />\n速彈基本功比較穩打穩實<br />\n<br />\n兩個都ear 同sightread 滿分咁制 ,<br />\n<br />\n呢兩part 都有少少難度高度, 特別係sightread 中間jam 野果五個bar 都幾刺激<br />\n<br />\n係短時間要分析key ,reading 同諗曲子, 犀利啊同學們<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNXMDq7mriYTUu248k2YyLNTdPftovnjdLjaaEAthK2YT?filename=3HAEBZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HAEBZj.jpg&h=55467945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUuQqfDwXoSBepjRamE9LzAA3ck3j1kDAT6aBzFoWAkRh?filename=6eRsLSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eRsLSE.jpg&h=0cd274e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下為每年紀錄<br />\n<br />\n2020 年出左兩個 8級, 琴行音樂治療個學生順利畢業, 佢的功課基本上都係我編<br />\n<br />\n多年教結他經驗,有學生已經做老師<br />\n<br />\n會教cover, jamming ,solo build up,各種style 同五線譜, 亦會有jazz standard , duo 咁教<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJazz 果邊會解唔同情景, 例如III7 用harmonic minor,轉調的SOLO 處理,alter scales ,dorian 的運用<br />\n會講點用同比住licks 學<br />\n<br />\n資歷: rockschool 8級電結他, 5級皇家鋼琴,五級樂理 地點: 青衣/荃灣<br />\n<br />\n實戰: 4年爵士大樂團, 一年兒童合唱團, jazz band 同各大大小小的酒店演出<br />\n<br />\n教學經驗: 2015 年 poly 音樂比賽冠軍 (份譜係我幫個學生編,幫佢執左個BASS,結他同鼓)<br />\n<br />\n聽個學生講佢地攞冠軍之後畀紅線簽咗約<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法: Tg :klguitar (第一堂試堂免費)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會注重講解唔同歌的solo idea, touching, 同睇五線譜,因為五線譜識分析好多野都read 得仔細好多..."},{"pid":"14e9681cce30d7726beb6674942e2824afc8493d","tid":2452832,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"連登r客 未死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faca35bcd37ccfa65ed3b7d3fa14d172c84bedc2","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"14e9681cce30d7726beb6674942e2824afc8493d","tid":2452832,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"連登r客 未死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"季季都比人罵嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n想令香港多d 人玩下jazz 又可以考到試<br />\n<br />\n係咁嫁啦...<br />\n<br />\n做到成績就得<br />\n<br />\n已慣被噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e167815d47b7dcc7c06d601dbb5ef5697774148","tid":2452832,"uid":308196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"有冇cover or example聽下"},{"pid":"ac5469f0cd295c51d4ff2e6c4e95262c539fafc3","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e167815d47b7dcc7c06d601dbb5ef5697774148","tid":2452832,"uid":308196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"有冇cover or example聽下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"Tg 我 比你睇吧<br />\n<br />\n一陣又比人噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd2a9ce3048bcc5fad960737711f67123c4a6d5","tid":2452832,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"全職教結他其實搵幾錢一個月，教琴行又要抽50%，又冇保障，又多人入行，到你年紀越大反而越黎越唔值錢，我見玩音樂既d一係有家底一係就好撚窮"},{"pid":"281cc545d0740c007acadc718bd432b85b77cf83","tid":2452832,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd2a9ce3048bcc5fad960737711f67123c4a6d5","tid":2452832,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"全職教結他其實搵幾錢一個月，教琴行又要抽50%，又冇保障，又多人入行，到你年紀越大反而越黎越唔值錢，我見玩音樂既d一係有家底一係就好撚窮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"真 見好多音樂人勁有錢 最尾found out大部分都係父幹撚<br />\n當然唔係勁top個d音樂人 因為top既音樂人真係搵好多錢"},{"pid":"cce93e8c7d433301f73d7cfa344ac0568cd53e04","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd2a9ce3048bcc5fad960737711f67123c4a6d5","tid":2452832,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"全職教結他其實搵幾錢一個月，教琴行又要抽50%，又冇保障，又多人入行，到你年紀越大反而越黎越唔值錢，我見玩音樂既d一係有家底一係就好撚窮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"睇你際遇嫁昨波<br />\n<br />\n不過又真係幾唔好做<br />\n<br />\n好多good player 都做到灰 <br />\n<br />\n一係for fun 做 一係轉工算<br />\n<br />\n又累又低人工又要受壓力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於結他手愈大愈唔值錢<br />\n<br />\n睇你肯唔肯繼續練野嫁姐<br />\n<br />\n彈jazz 果堆樂理咪愈彈愈識囉<br />\n<br />\n反而愈老愈勁wor <br />\n<br />\nRock player就慘d<br />\n<br />\n真係會操到手痛腰痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做得呢行 做左十年都係大部分係愛<br />\n<br />\n同 講笑咁講<br />\n<br />\n係貢獻自己"},{"pid":"f274972ae16db4ff4d359f8d4ae8f2dfab102176","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"281cc545d0740c007acadc718bd432b85b77cf83","tid":2452832,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd2a9ce3048bcc5fad960737711f67123c4a6d5","tid":2452832,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"全職教結他其實搵幾錢一個月，教琴行又要抽50%，又冇保障，又多人入行，到你年紀越大反而越黎越唔值錢，我見玩音樂既d一係有家底一係就好撚窮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"真 見好多音樂人勁有錢 最尾found out大部分都係父幹撚<br />\n當然唔係勁top個d音樂人 因為top既音樂人真係搵好多錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:55:09.000Z","msg":"做job 做伴奏打上去<br />\n<br />\n會結果發現 愈上流 基本上都係外國music school 俱樂部<br />\n<br />\n個個屋企肯花 百幾二百萬 去讀書<br />\n<br />\n最尾係 人地生活本身好過你 又技術好過你<br />\n<br />\nTheory backup 又好過你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過jazz 果邊又好d 的<br />\n<br />\n早幾年同fd 組左隊jazz band mate <br />\n<br />\n之後跟有jazz party <br />\n<br />\n咪一班人膽粗粗 去玩<br />\n<br />\n雖然做唔到最上流不過中流都ok<br />\n<br />\njazz standard 大部分歌都carry 到 同hold 到個場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會眼見而家除左rock 都開始有唔同導師教standard 歌<br />\n<br />\n見到d 生面後生call autumn leaves 都幾funny haha<br />\n<br />\n十年前 jazz 只係超小眾玩 來來去去果堆<br />\n<br />\n再加果時少人識free jam ， 不過而家已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過jazz party 最尾都係大魚食細魚<br />\n<br />\n最尾連中流都搞唔店<br />\n<br />\n因為d神人 鮑以正， ted lo 果d 上台彈<br />\n<br />\n佢地d rhythm 會複雜到你頂唔到/ 唔慣<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地好鼓勵後生去玩<br />\n<br />\n不過內心都怯兩怯就真haha"},{"pid":"bdabfc4db276b15fe0dead247dfc73a1c4225e4a","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"每期開POST都會分享下一D 教學間學生經常卡關的問題<br />\n今次都繼續分享一D 比較有用的分析<br />\n<br />\n今次用Jason Kui - reactive impulse 入面bar 43 一句好型的句子<br />\n來講野rock licks 的句構<br />\nFirst step<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd1W1Wd1nsebZB3NvmY5FR29Z8FufisopDjQsTs76ada7?filename=W1Ssrsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Ssrsu.jpg&h=3e906860&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢呢句有用主體想用的main theme - power chord add 9 <br />\n+一句比較難分析的min 7 arpeggios<br />\n<br />\n咁我慢慢再講埋arpeggios 點寫點理解同點運用啦<br />\n<br />\n今次主講chord power 的advanced use<br />\n<br />\nRoot on 6 string<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVKVyV6Qd3E1EtRv3pLsmfhZ4JJ6h7fpHH2bd8TKgrox?filename=UPhcCzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPhcCzF.png&h=9a9bfa0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRoot on 5 string<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY4G5zQTGfTqC7Vgun2fE8VH3b2XzRb2ax49S1a6iJkXP?filename=3P3bS72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P3bS72.png&h=428ae585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩岩學電結他就一定會學下D power chord 掃掃掃<br />\n然後學的時侯一定要知點解個POWER chord 咁來<br />\n或者何謂power chord<br />\n<br />\n個jason kui 呢句的case就係橫向彈power chord add9 再加一組arpeggios<br />\n<br />\npower chord 係個高8度位度Add9 如圖示<br />\n(add9 可理解為8度RE)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\npower chord 除左可以理解為scale board 的衍生品<br />\n亦可以由bar chord 的附屬品<br />\n如下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV3o6pF1jC9hsGkSydwbqmfAcL883Jh2dbjcteet3Z2V2?filename=VSWEhAD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSWEhAD.png&h=0a58feab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁, 下次再打下power chord 的來由同chord progression 的運作<br />\n<br />\n呢個係上個post 講scale ,調性同jamming 的基礎野<br />\n有興趣的朋友可以睇番上post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787577</a>"},{"pid":"6030be268a32b8e0c02d30216119a39193802efb","tid":2452832,"uid":126466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"收幾錢先？"},{"pid":"dd85b442c67ad55b8394aee0e7b8827309773504","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6030be268a32b8e0c02d30216119a39193802efb","tid":2452832,"uid":126466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"收幾錢先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"正常價錢<br />\n<br />\n有趣tg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac0a22c99f8610c839a7a2a2b95fe2e7f04e724","tid":2452832,"uid":40537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"bass教唔教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec05315d3516f5053be1553b61dbfcbe48e0880a","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac0a22c99f8610c839a7a2a2b95fe2e7f04e724","tid":2452832,"uid":40537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"bass教唔教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"Bass 唔識 唔教<br />\n<br />\n不過可以介紹神人session lv bass 你學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個樂手Mainly jazz"},{"pid":"d89768839f0f6e4e79aaeec5a2b31737356de599","tid":2452832,"uid":74305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"jazz drum有冇老師介紹"},{"pid":"904836f9d95b170635d1d42d941ddb344081bad4","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89768839f0f6e4e79aaeec5a2b31737356de599","tid":2452832,"uid":74305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"jazz drum有冇老師介紹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"Bossa , funky , jazz standard 類？<br />\n<br />\n有啊 酒吧jamming party 都遇好幾個"},{"pid":"848789d8e03f33dd91ee101bd5079459b653b6f8","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T19:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00409a173bfa8ce0d32c5726dc20d338b8f226b","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"偶爾一推 考試月又好忙<br />\n<br />\n考生請加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31fb6c700c3832cb97ed65083b05d0732b89f45","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8e76b62eb3ba9cf87035acc378425aed9150c1","tid":2452832,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0